I think I used to be easily distracted with my thoughts even when there’s something that needs to be done right at that moment. When I get involved in something or somebody, it can consume all my thoughts, energy, time and feelings, good or bad. Then when the time comes that I shouldn’t be having those thoughts and feelings about whatever the thing] or person that has captured and consumed all my thoughts and feeling are not around, the same feelings or thoughts just come crawling up and running through my head over and over again.
